room_title: Escape room "The Labyrinth" by Trapped! Escape Room in Cleveland
room_description: Legend speaks of the edge of the world, a place only the gods have seen, where eternal life can be obtained. After years of searching, you have come this close, yet the Labyrinth stands in your way. Solve its puzzles and progress to the Tree of Life, or run out of time and be trapped in the maze forever.
